<h2>Crossbow released - 10/9/09</h2>
<ul>
   <li><a href="./crossbow">Crossbow</a> is a cloud-computing pipeline for whole genome resequencing. 
  It combines Bowtie and <a href="http://soap.genomics.org.cn/soapsnp.html">SoapSNP</a>, an accurate
