<h2>0.9.8 release - 11/25/08</h2>
  <ul>
  <li><tt>--unfa</tt>/<tt>--unfq &lt;filename&gt;</tt> options cause bowtie to dump unaligned
      reads to FASTA and/or FASTQ files.</li>
  <li><tt>bowtie-build</tt> now selects its memory-efficiency parameters (<tt>--bmax</tt>,
